features: Slide Rail Design: The maximum distance of sliding forward is 95MM, and the maximum distance of sliding backward is 90MM.

Stable Structure: The vehicle seat lifting base is made of steel alloy material, which is strong, very durable and has a solid structure.
Practical: The universal seat adjuster allows you to adjust the seat position according to your needs and adjust it to a comfortable position.
Easy Installation: The seat height riser is easy to install and use. After removing the original seat base, replace the lifting base and fix it.
